&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AI/ML systems, data infrastructure, or high-performance computing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of building or contributing to widely used systems, platforms, or tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
